Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}該去採訪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好好 你真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是直播 還可以重來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的搖了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有說過海浪會越來越兇猛的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把握好時間 人家說後面還會我們幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼不叫醒我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}叫過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不狠狠地叫 我醒不來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下等一下 再給我30分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不對 15分鐘就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我們在外面等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她沒有眉毛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很多女生都會修掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那才比較普通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們往南走的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會在海上幾處稱為「站點」的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收集微生物和海水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為此船上搭載了不少有用的器材
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是採水器和溫鹽深儀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哇 這就是…採水器…和溫鹽深儀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:30.70,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}採集這類礦石的同時 要調查南極的地質情況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}移開點 移開點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}麥克風太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:33.41,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}調查地底數公里的地質層
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:36.13,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來研究遠古時期地球的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個人倒是留著眉毛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你聽人家說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}糟了糟了糟了 遲到了遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}該往哪邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:53.18,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康布丁體W7\fs25\bord1\1c&H3C4041&\3c&H4D5F63&\pos(316,276)}女高中生的房間{\i1}！！{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:53.18,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康布丁體W7\fs25\bord1\1c&H3C4041&\3c&H4D5F63&\pos(352,444)}進門前先{\fn華康POP1體W7\1c&H48E8E4&}敲門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯嗯 等你們好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦 甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡也能做甜點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然只是用手頭的材料做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就麻煩你們處理那些啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那些？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我才說要帶削皮器的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鈴這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有這麼多沒削啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過這種事做起來真開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理很喜歡機械式作業啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們四個加起來才剛過一馬力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很慢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反正知道你們在家不幫家務啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過慢就慢點 別急
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別傷到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我畢竟是專業的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是職業廚師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}平時是食堂阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}常面對跟你們一樣挑三揀四的顧客
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又要考慮菜單又要下廚做菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們加油 早點學會怎麼搭船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼搭船？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:15.64,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天一一〇〇至一七〇〇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:18.35,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}船上跑步訓練 逆時針跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以在船上跑步了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是說 我們可以出去運動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}運動？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}削完了就帶你們出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}運動也算隊員的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要在這裡跑步嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}廣播裡說順時針 就是這個方向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說逆時針就是反方向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不同的日子跑的方向不一樣 要注意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概要跑多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這沒有絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過你們也聽過不少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}觀測隊隊員比拼的就是體能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有時得在零下幾十度的環境下作業一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}記住這點 好好鍛鍊自己就行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽以前也總是會運動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為體能不足而累倒 不僅是自己什麼都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還會要旁邊的人出手來幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都到南極了 你們也不想當拖油瓶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 我們也加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理還沒搞清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她很快就會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼…這麼…大啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在這裡走過很多圈了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…大家都差不多這個速度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個人居然也能跑這麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}外表是個女科學家 體能卻相當不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等…慢著啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}18
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從南極回去的時候 我們要變成亞馬遜女戰士了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪有那麼容易當
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 最後一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好癢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鼻頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結月 難道你手抬不起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要是敢做什麼 我可不會放過你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:55.51,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康隸書體W5\1c&H3B3836&\3c&HD1DDEE&\frz1.134\pos(542,150)}不會放過你♡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你白癡嗎 你白癡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:08:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是海水浴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}浴缸挺大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}值得一泡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能快點出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}海水的刺激性比想像中強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}頭髮都變粗糙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以大家才剪頭髮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}男的都剃成了光頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 那我們也剪掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我來幫你剪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}船上有理髮的工具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地球粉碎了也不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}同上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼 我還挺會剪的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}經常修自己的瀏海
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謎團終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}解開了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以才是那個髮型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}準備用餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}該吃晚餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會吧 這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:48.23,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn@華康特粗楷體\b0\bord0\1c&H60514C&\pos(608,464)\frx356\fry46\frz259.5}用餐時 黑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:48.23,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn@華康特粗楷體\b0\1c&H60514C&\3c&HEBEDE8&\frx358\fry40\pos(496,260)\frz263.3}沒飯牌請找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}渾身黏答答的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是你沒有好好沖澡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為沒時間了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}馬鈴薯燉肉 是我們削皮的那些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有什麼忘記做的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吃飯 洗澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}洗衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個還沒有定好時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還不是日向你們洗澡的時候在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}負責去洗完再來吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等 飯都不給吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但當初因為可能會忘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以定好誰值日的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我記得是大家猜拳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.73,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康中特圓體\bord0\1vc(&H929A90&,&H929A90&,&H494D49&,&H494D49&)\frx350\fry340\frz9.372\pos(586,50)}洗衣間 浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.73,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康楷書體W5\bord0\b0\be1\1c&H85734D&\frz3.398\pos(708,268)\frx344\fry358}關於淡水的使用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.73,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康特粗楷體\bord0\fs25\1c&H808885&\pos(544,362)\frz2.28}綜合訓練期間允許使用淡水洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.73,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康特粗楷體\bord0\fs25\1c&H808885&\frz2.28\pos(588,438)}（用海水洗也行哦~）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.73,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康楷書體W7\bord0\1c&H2A3989&\pos(604,542)\frz359\frx2\fry354}努力省水喔♡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行什麼行啦 結果還不是吃飽飯才洗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來得及不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定累壞了吧 比預想中忙多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是啦 明天開始也是一樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}撐得住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能努力吧 也沒有選擇的餘地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好噁心…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺…好噁心…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:15.44,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@華康儷中黑\fs22\1c&H271DB2&\3c&HA5B5BC&\frz271.1\t(0,5520,0\frz267.1)\frx4\fry6\move(1086,358,1104,374,33,5497)}上完廁所後 請將此閥門逆時針旋轉沖水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:15.44,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@華康儷中黑\fs22\1c&H271DB2&\3c&HA5B5BC&\frz271.1\t(0,5520,0\frz267.1)\frx4\fry6\move(964,360,984,376,33,5497)}沖完後將閥門關緊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}世界在旋轉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別說話 一說話就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別問了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們暈船好嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是之前完全沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}暈船藥也吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是藥效過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}畢竟是藥嘛 藥效早晚會過的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊 從來沒坐過這麼久的交通工具
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以沒想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼怪我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吃完藥好好睡一覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有就是要好好吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們大概沒什麼食慾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}覺得吃了也會吐出來 所以不想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是不吃飯 體力會越來越跟不上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最後會變成要靠吊點滴來補充營養
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到了那個地步 再怎麼鍛鍊也沒有意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}準備用餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}佳苗小姐不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果不想在南極扯後腿 就要逼自己吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全部吐光了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結月也全吐光了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}求求你別晃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一下子就好 快停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在好像停下來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像是要採集海水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這也叫停…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然弓子小姐說漸漸會習慣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是根本沒有習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:15.81,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康少女文字W5\bord0\fs30\t(0,6520,0\fs35)\1c&H4B534F&\frz5.252\move(544,150,436,58,0,6497)}優勝隊伍的獎勵！\N等待您說出願望！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:15.81,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康少女文字W5\bord0\fs45\t(0,6520,0\fs50)\1c&H4B534F&\frz6.777\move(278,200,134,112,33,6497)}請踴躍報名♡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:15.81,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康少女文字W5\bord0\fs35\t(0,6520,0\fs40)\1c&H2E1999&\frz8.079\move(16,364,-156,312,33,6497)}想要獲得優勝的隊員請自備\N已經發給各位的瑞士刀參加
