Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:34.12,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}前景雖不明朗 但我已決心邁開雙腿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:52.48,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}好奇心與你 牽起了我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:21:00.48,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}溫柔的聲音與眼神 指引著我新的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:05.36,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}邁出這一步 就是啟程的訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:08.83,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}邁出下一步 我們將走遍四方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:13.25,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}向遠方 向遠方 向陌生的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:16.00,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}我們都要一起前行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:19.34,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}邁出這一步 拋下作繭自縛的殼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:22.67,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}邁出下一步 踏向久久尋求的光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:27.68,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}沒錯呀 就今天 向陌生的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:33.77,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}一步又一步又一步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一片漆黑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們要穿越這片海域啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去那片被狂風大浪保護的冰原大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們選擇了去那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼 雨水？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好鹹 這是海浪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:19:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好鹹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恢復精神了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是 精力充沛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為昨天還看到了鯨魚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終於學會搭船了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只不過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等你們下了陸地 又會暈陸地了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}左10度 5海浬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在哪在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}萬里無雲 見不到鳥兒飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}身邊只有無垠的碧波蕩漾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遙望遠眺 也只有地平線的蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}船聲浪聲傳入耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但看到這片絕景 彷彿天地間安靜了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的眼前便是宇宙一般寧靜的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這一刻我相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極就在視線的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在打開大門前 還有一大段旅程呢
Comment: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:23.73,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}長いトンネルの出口を探していた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:34.66,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}かすかな光の匂いがしてる方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:40.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}間違っても　笑えるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:51.26,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}ここから始めよう　僕は旅に出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:23:01.98,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}汚れた真ん丸のビー玉　握りしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:13.28,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}言えなかった言葉も　きっと見つかるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.41,0:23:18.87,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}バカにされたって構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:24.21,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}信じてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:23.73,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}尋找著漫長隧道的出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:34.66,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}向著泛著微光氣味的方向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:40.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}就算走錯了 也別忘了微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:51.26,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}從這裡開始 我將踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:23:01.98,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}緊緊捏住手心裡 髒髒的玻璃珠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:13.28,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}沒說出口的話 我也一定會找到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.41,0:23:18.87,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}隨你們嘲笑吧 我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:24.21,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}要相信自己 邁出腳步
